						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone built into the platform in front of the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1440.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged and effaced record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1362, Raudri, Bhādrapada, śu. 11, Tuesday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1440, September 6, Tuesday, f.d.t. ·92.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription seems to record a gift of land by certain individuals.</p>						

						</summary>
